vqAMW8.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>다음으로는, 데이터 스트림 설정이다. 데이터 스트림으라는 말이 좀 생소할 수 있는데, 데이터 관점에서 데이터소스라고 보는 것이 적절해 보인다. 여기에서 대상 사이트/블로그의 URL주소 값을 입력해 주고, 이름도 지정해 주자. 그 다음 스트림 만들기를 선택한다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5b500bef4e245358a057dc6b3ef92177/eb2af/image-20210531214700285.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.24324324324324%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20210531214700285\"\n        title=\"image-20210531214700285\"\n        src=\"/static/5b500bef4e245358a057dc6b3ef92177/fcda8/image-20210531214700285.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5b500bef4e245358a057dc6b3ef92177/12f09/image-20210531214700285.png 148w,\n/static/5b500bef4e245358a057dc6b3ef92177/e4a3f/image-20210531214700285.png 295w,\n/static/5b500bef4e245358a057dc6b3ef92177/fcda8/image-20210531214700285.png 590w,\n/static/5b500bef4e245358a057dc6b3ef92177/efc66/image-20210531214700285.png 885w,\n/static/5b500bef4e245358a057dc6b3ef92177/eb2af/image-20210531214700285.png 954w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>필자는 블로그의 URL을 입력하고, 스트림 이름은 My Tech Blog라고 입력하였다. 스트림 생성을 마치고 나면, 하단에 태그에 대한 가이드가 있다. \"새로운 온페이지 태그 추가\"를 눌러서 태그 적용 가이드를 살펴 보자. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/37b7d5c4c4b561db06dc5b82fe709d30/264eb/image-20210531214753440.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20210531214753440\"\n        title=\"image-20210531214753440\"\n        src=\"/static/37b7d5c4c4b561db06dc5b82fe709d30/fcda8/image-20210531214753440.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/37b7d5c4c4b561db06dc5b82fe709d30/12f09/image-20210531214753440.png 148w,\n/static/37b7d5c4c4b561db06dc5b82fe709d30/e4a3f/image-20210531214753440.png 295w,\n/static/37b7d5c4c4b561db06dc5b82fe709d30/fcda8/image-20210531214753440.png 590w,\n/static/37b7d5c4c4b561db06dc5b82fe709d30/264eb/image-20210531214753440.png 867w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음은 \"새로운 온페이지 태그 추가\"를 눌렀을 때 제공되는 구글의 공식 스크립트 이다. </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>기존 온페이지 태그 사용은 과거 버전이다. GA ID가 \"UA-xxxx\"로 되어 있는 코드들은 기존 태그를 사용한다. 필자는 새롭게 적용된 태그를 사용하였다. </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cf66a7264583b1cf8e43d538bd05be3c/8b69f/image-20210531214849829.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.16216216216216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20210531214849829\"\n        title=\"image-20210531214849829\"\n        src=\"/static/cf66a7264583b1cf8e43d538bd05be3c/fcda8/image-20210531214849829.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cf66a7264583b1cf8e43d538bd05be3c/12f09/image-20210531214849829.png 148w,\n/static/cf66a7264583b1cf8e43d538bd05be3c/e4a3f/image-20210531214849829.png 295w,\n/static/cf66a7264583b1cf8e43d538bd05be3c/fcda8/image-20210531214849829.png 590w,\n/static/cf66a7264583b1cf8e43d538bd05be3c/efc66/image-20210531214849829.png 885w,\n/static/cf66a7264583b1cf8e43d538bd05be3c/8b69f/image-20210531214849829.png 912w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이제 위에서 제공되는 태그만 자신의 웹사이트/블로그의 모든 페이지에 적용될 수 있도록 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;</code>  태그에 삽입해 주면 된다. </p>\n<h1 id=\"구글애널리틱스-설정-하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%EA%B8%80%EC%95%A0%EB%84%90%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"구글애널리틱스 설정 하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구글애널리틱스 설정 하기</h1>\n<p>우리는 지금까지 Gatsby를 사용한 정적웹사이트로 이야기를 이끌어 왔다. 따라서, GA 적용 스크립트를 Gatsby Layout 또는 Helmet에 적용하면 될 것이다. </p>\n<p>그런데, React 또는 Gatsby의 JSX에 저 스크립트를 바로 입력하면 다음과 같은 에러를 보게 될것이다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e2e156652b8a33035a96db05ddfdd251/3996e/bMH_EUfbu7SI_g54nhc3zE3IVVJlQo-QUb7cJ0TsSMCYemyp0TY7M_yM1BDvVHW9lFAec4MnIegZ4mfng_qYOaRWzn_shsAI-orSHkI6rQW5o1lm64QDAZmroW6MYIyiy1R8LMryzVw.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.810810810810814%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/e2e156652b8a33035a96db05ddfdd251/fcda8/bMH_EUfbu7SI_g54nhc3zE3IVVJlQo-QUb7cJ0TsSMCYemyp0TY7M_yM1BDvVHW9lFAec4MnIegZ4mfng_qYOaRWzn_shsAI-orSHkI6rQW5o1lm64QDAZmroW6MYIyiy1R8LMryzVw.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e2e156652b8a33035a96db05ddfdd251/12f09/bMH_EUfbu7SI_g54nhc3zE3IVVJlQo-QUb7cJ0TsSMCYemyp0TY7M_yM1BDvVHW9lFAec4MnIegZ4mfng_qYOaRWzn_shsAI-orSHkI6rQW5o1lm64QDAZmroW6MYIyiy1R8LMryzVw.png 148w,\n/static/e2e156652b8a33035a96db05ddfdd251/e4a3f/bMH_EUfbu7SI_g54nhc3zE3IVVJlQo-QUb7cJ0TsSMCYemyp0TY7M_yM1BDvVHW9lFAec4MnIegZ4mfng_qYOaRWzn_shsAI-orSHkI6rQW5o1lm64QDAZmroW6MYIyiy1R8LMryzVw.png 295w,\n/static/e2e156652b8a33035a96db05ddfdd251/fcda8/bMH_EUfbu7SI_g54nhc3zE3IVVJlQo-QUb7cJ0TsSMCYemyp0TY7M_yM1BDvVHW9lFAec4MnIegZ4mfng_qYOaRWzn_shsAI-orSHkI6rQW5o1lm64QDAZmroW6MYIyiy1R8LMryzVw.png 590w,\n/static/e2e156652b8a33035a96db05ddfdd251/3996e/bMH_EUfbu7SI_g54nhc3zE3IVVJlQo-QUb7cJ0TsSMCYemyp0TY7M_yM1BDvVHW9lFAec4MnIegZ4mfng_qYOaRWzn_shsAI-orSHkI6rQW5o1lm64QDAZmroW6MYIyiy1R8LMryzVw.png 648w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>JSX가 순수 Html 처럼 보이지만 사실은 그렇지 않기 때문에, JSX를 html로 생성하는 과정에서 WEBPACK이 에러를 발생한다. </p>\n<p>React에서는 이렇게 순수 Html 입력을 위해서 <code class=\"language-text\">InnerHTML</code> 을 입력할 수 있는 기능을 별도 가지고 있다. 필자는 아래와 같이 GA 삽입용 Component를 별도로 만들어서 사용하고 있다. (아래는 Component를 만드는데 사용한 Typescript 이다. )</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">GaProps</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  ga_id<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Ga</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">props<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> GaProps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> ga_id <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> htmlContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  &lt;script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>ga_id<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\">&lt;/script>\n  &lt;script>\n    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n    gtag('js', new Date());\n\n    gtag('config', '</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>ga_id<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">');\n  &lt;/script>\n  </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div\n      id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'GaContainer'</span>\n      dangerouslySetInnerHTML<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>__html<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>htmlContent<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Ga<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Ga Compoent를 생성하였다면, 실제 파일에 다음과 같이 적용하였다. 유의할 점은 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Helmet&gt;</code> 태그 내부에 하지않고, Html에의 Body 부분에 생성하였다는 점이다. 이것은 <code class=\"language-text\">Ga Componet</code> 를 생성할 때 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div&gt;</code> 태그를 사용하였기 때문이다. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Ga <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'../GA'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n\n <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Helmet<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>link rel<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"shortcut icon\"</span> href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"favicon.ico\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>link rel<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"icon\"</span> href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"favicon.ico\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>link rel<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"icon\"</span> type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"image/png\"</span> href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"favicon.ico\"</span> sizes<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"16x16\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>meta name<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"google-site-verification\"</span> content<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>googleSearchConsole <span class=\"token operator\">??</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Helmet<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n\t\t  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"layout\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Ga ga_id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>googleAnalytics <span class=\"token operator\">??</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n      \t<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  </code></pre></div>\n<p>구글 애널리틱스의 화면에서 실시간 사용자에 숫자가 증가 하는 것을 확인 하면, 최종 확인된 것이다. GA적용 후 바로 커밋하고 접속하면 자신이 접속한 이력이 카운트 되어서 기존 <code class=\"language-text\">0</code>에서 숫자 <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>로 변경됨을 확인하자. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 327px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ebd267ab8be1f995eedf2d7ecf5d35a7/00e65/image-20210531215628535.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.54054054054053%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image-20210531215628535\"\n        title=\"image-20210531215628535\"\n        src=\"/static/ebd267ab8be1f995eedf2d7ecf5d35a7/00e65/image-20210531215628535.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ebd267ab8be1f995eedf2d7ecf5d35a7/12f09/image-20210531215628535.png 148w,\n/static/ebd267ab8be1f995eedf2d7ecf5d35a7/e4a3f/image-20210531215628535.png 295w,\n/static/ebd267ab8be1f995eedf2d7ecf5d35a7/00e65/image-20210531215628535.png 327w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 327px) 100vw, 327px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","excerpt":"…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsbyBlog_6/#%EB%82%98%EB%A7%8C%EC%9D%98-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%8B%A4-%EC%A2%8B%EC%9D%80%EB%8D%B0\">나만의 블로그. 다 좋은데....</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsbyBlog_6/#%EB%B0%A9%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EB%B6%84%EC%84%9D-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5%EC%9D%B4-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%98%EB%8B%A4\">방문자 분석 기능이 필요하다.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsbyBlog_6/#%EA%B5%AC%EA%B8%80-%EC%95%A0%EB%84%90%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B1%EC%8A%A4ga--google-analytics\">구글 애널리틱스(GA : Google Analytics)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsbyBlog_6/#%EA%B5%AC%EA%B8%80%EC%95%A0%EB%84%90%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B1%EC%8A%A4-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">구글애널리틱스 설정 하기</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_6/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"블로그에 사용자 분석기능을 달자 (ft. GoogleAnalytics)","date":"May 31, 2021","tags":["gatsby","blog","GoogleAnalytics"],"keywords":["gatsby","make blog","github blog","사용자분석","Google Analytics","구글 애널리틱스","방문자분석","Gatsby 블로그 만들기","블로그 만들기","정적사이트 만들기","구글 블로그 분석"],"category":"blog","update":"May 31, 2021","titleImage":"gatsbyCover.png"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/windstream/my_dev/blog/sjwind/gatsby/markdown/blog/gatsbyBlog_6.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_6/","series":[{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_1/","title":"개츠비(Gatsby)로 정적웹사이트 및 블로그 만들기 1","num":1},{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_2/","title":"개츠비(Gatsby) + Git Page로 자신만의 블로그 만들기","num":2},{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_3/","title":"gatsby 3","num":3},{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_4/","title":"웹사이트 아이콘 파비콘 (Favicon) 만들기 - 파비콘 마스터 하기","num":4},{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_5/","title":"블로그에 댓글기능 달아주기 (ft.Disqus 붙이기)","num":5},{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_6/","title":"블로그에 사용자 분석기능을 달자 (ft. GoogleAnalytics)","num":6},{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_7/","title":"Gatsby Netlify에 호스팅하기","num":7},{"slug":"/gatsbyBlog_8/","title":"배경 이미지 꾸미기 (ft. Parallax)","num":8}],"lastmod":"2021-05-31"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","3998623811","63159454"]}